{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>设有N×N的方格图，我们在其中的某些方格中填入正整数，而其它的方格中则放入数字0。如下图所示：<p><p>![](pic/1303.gif)<p><p>某人从图中的左上角A出发，可以向下行走，也可以向右行走，直到到达右下角的B点。在走过的路上，他可以取走方格中的数（取走后的方格中将变为数字0）。<p><p>此人从A点到B点共走了两次，试找出两条这样的路径，使得取得的数字和为最大。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"方格取数 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>第一个整数，表示两条路径上取得的最大的和。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行为一个整数N（N≤10），表示N×N的方格图。<p><p>接下来的每行有三个整数，第一个为行号数，第二个为列号数，第三个为在该行、该列上所放的数。一行“0 0 0”表示结束。<p>","examples":"<input>8\n2 3 13\n2 6 6\n3 5 7\n4 4 14\n5 2 21\n5 6 4\n6 3 15\n7 2 14\n0 0 0\n</input><output>67\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1277","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}